In your meta elements for all the open graph you specified, you missed the namespace to **ogp** which is indicated with the use of the prefix element: `prefix=&quot;og: http://ogp.me/ns#&quot;`. Check out the example from the **[Open Graph guide][1]**:

&lt;!-- begin snippet: js hide: false console: true babel: false --&gt;

&lt;!-- language: lang-html --&gt;

    &lt;html prefix=&quot;og: http://ogp.me/ns#&quot;&gt;
    &lt;head&gt;
    &lt;title&gt;The Rock (1996)&lt;/title&gt;
    &lt;meta property=&quot;og:title&quot; content=&quot;The Rock&quot; /&gt;
    &lt;meta property=&quot;og:type&quot; content=&quot;video.movie&quot; /&gt;
    &lt;meta property=&quot;og:url&quot; content=&quot;http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0117500/&quot; /&gt;
    &lt;meta property=&quot;og:image&quot; content=&quot;http://ia.media-imdb.com/images/rock.jpg&quot; /&gt;
    ...
    &lt;/head&gt;
    ...
    &lt;/html&gt;

&lt;!-- end snippet --&gt;

Thus, your meta elements do not have a link to the library to determine their values. The following syntax may help for your markup: 

&lt;!-- begin snippet: js hide: false console: true babel: false --&gt;

&lt;!-- language: lang-html --&gt;

    &lt;!DOCTYPE html prefix=&quot;og: http://ogp.me/ns#&quot;&gt;
    &lt;html lang=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
        &lt;head&gt;
            &lt;meta charset=&quot;UTF-8&quot;&gt;
            &lt;!-- Primary Meta Tags --&gt;
            &lt;title&gt;This is sample title&lt;/title&gt;

            &lt;!-- Open Graph / Facebook / LinkedIn --&gt;
            &lt;meta property=&quot;og:type&quot; content=&quot;website&quot;&gt;
            &lt;meta property=&quot;og:title&quot; content=&quot;This is sample title&quot;&gt;
            &lt;meta property=&quot;og:description&quot; content=&#39;sample description&#39;&gt;
            &lt;meta property=&quot;og:image&quot; content=&quot;image path&quot;&gt;

        &lt;/head&gt;
        &lt;body&gt;&lt;/body&gt;
    &lt;/html&gt;

&lt;!-- end snippet --&gt;

  [1]: https://ogp.me/

